      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国承诺提供支持，防止建筑商的困境蔓延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-29/korea-mulls-billions-more-support-as-builder-suffers-debt-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国官员承诺，如果需要限制建筑商债务问题的溢出效应，将加强一项 660 亿美元的计划来稳定市场，央行警告明年房地产风险可能会增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-29/korea-mulls-billions-more-support-as-builder-suffers-debt-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 01:34:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于 OPEC+ 和战争未能阻止年度油价下跌，油价在 2024 年举步维艰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-29</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于战争和 OPEC+ 减产未能提振价格，油价将出现 2020 年以来最大年度跌幅，交易商担心未来几个季度全球原油供应可能仍超过需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-29</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 00:21:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着资本外流缓解，2024 年人民币兑美元有望升值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-29/yuan-seen-rising-versus-dollar-in-2024-as-capital-outflows-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的一项调查显示，随着利差缩小缓解资本外流，人民币将在 2024 年出现三年来的首次升值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-29/yuan-seen-rising-versus-dollar-in-2024-as-capital-outflows-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
